<p>$(2)~F_1 = F_2$</p>

<p>$(3)~F_2 . cos \beta = F \implies F = F_2 . cos \beta = F_1 . cos \beta = \dfrac{\tau . cos \beta}{l_{DC} . sin \alpha}$</p>
